AWSCloudTrail
| where TimeGenerated > ago(90d)
| where isnotempty(UserIdentityAccessKeyId)
| summarize
    FirstSeen=min(TimeGenerated),
    LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated),
    IPs=make_set(SourceIPAddress),
    GeoCount=dcount(AwsRegion)
    by UserIdentityUserName, UserIdentityAccessKeyId
| extend KeyAgeDays = datetime_diff("day", now(), FirstSeen)
| where KeyAgeDays > 90 and GeoCount > 2

Geographic spread + long-lived trust = ideal attacker dwell time.
